n proof document had wrong format — had to be rewritten to match expected `## AC N: Title` format.\n42\t\n43\t### Severity Distribution\n44\t\n45\t| Severity | Count | Fixed? |\n46\t|----------|-------|--------|\n47\t| HIGH | 1 | Yes |\n48\t| MEDIUM | 3 | 2 fixed, 1 deferred (package.json stale entries) |\n49\t| LOW | 2 | Deferred (stubs, dead test suites) |\n50\t\n51\t---\n52\t\n53\t## Cost Analysis\n54\t\n55\t### Session Tool Usage (This Session Only — Story 1-2 Review + Verification)\n56\t\n57\t`codeharness stats` could not run — ralph/session-logs directory was deleted as part of story 1-2. Cost data is reconstructed from subagent token reports in the session issues log.\n58\t\n59\t**Code Review phase (1-2):**\n60\t\n61\t| Tool | Calls |\n62\t|------|-------|\n63\t| Bash | 12 |\n64\t| Read | 13 |\n65\t| Edit | 8 |\n66\t| Grep | 3 |\n67\t| Glob | 4 |\n68\t| Skill | 1 |\n69\t| **Total** | **29** |\n70\t\n71\tLargest Bash outputs: `git diff --name-only` (~250 lines), `git ls-files ralph/` (~250 lines), `git status --porcelain` (~80 lines).\n72\t\n73\t**Verification phase (1-2):**\n74\t\n75\t| Tool | Calls |\n76\t|------|-------|\n77\t| Bash | 14 |\n78\t| Read | 3 |\n79\t| Grep | 4 |\n80\t| Write | 1 |"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01VAEQjRryBmGfP8NazPmeVv","session_id":"90f775a4-0bf0-4884-b410-4d7f1f50684d","uuid":"a5ccc348-1adf-44a3-9ff6-d82844e828b7","timestamp":"2026-04-03T08:22:52.719Z"}
